This project (mcp-etf-holdings) is an independent open source tool and is not affiliated with,
endorsed by, or supported by Yahoo Finance or yfinance.

Financial data is retrieved at runtime from Yahoo Finance via the yfinance library
(https://github.com/ranaroussi/yfinance), which is licensed under the Apache License 2.0.
yfinance is listed as a runtime dependency and its code is not included in this repository.

